"next-steps\">Next steps\u003C/h2>\u003Ca class=\"sl-anchor-link\" href=\"#next-steps\">\u003Cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"sl-anchor-icon\">\u003Csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\u003Cpath fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"sr-only\" data-pagefind-ignore=\"\">Section titled “Next steps”\u003C/span>\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cp>Head to the \u003Ca href=\"/guides/quickstart/\">Quick Start\u003C/a> guide to get Aether running locally.\u003C/p>",{"headings":20,"localImagePaths":31,"remoteImagePaths":32,"frontmatter":33,"imagePaths":34},[21,25,28],{"depth":22,"slug":23,"text":24},2,"why-aether","Why Aether?",{"depth":22,"slug":26,"text":27},"architecture","Architecture",{"depth":22,"slug":29,"text":30},"next-steps","Next steps",[],[],{"title":6,"description":7},[],"guides/quickstart",{"id":35,"data":37,"body":43,"filePath":44,"digest":45,"rendered":46},{"title":38,"description":39,"editUrl":8,"head":40,"template":10,"sidebar":41,"pagefind":8,"draft":12},"Quick Start","Get Aether running locally in minutes.",[],{"hidden":12,"attrs":42},{},"## Prerequisites\n\n- Rust 1.80+ (install via [rustup](https://rustup.rs))\n- An API key for at least one LLM provider (Anthropic, OpenRouter, etc.)\n\n## Clone and build\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/joshka/aether.git\ncd aether\ncargo build\n```\n\n## Run the TUI\n\n```bash\ncargo run --bin wisp\n```\n\n## Run headless\n\n```bash\ncargo run --bin aether -- --headless \"Your prompt here\"\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nAether reads MCP server configuration from `.mcp.json` in your project root. See the [Introduction](/guides/introduction/) for an overview of the architecture.","src/content/docs/guides/quickstart.md","961ba0fbcc167e48",{"html":47,"metadata":48},"\u003Cdiv class=\"sl-heading-wrapper level-h2\">\u003Ch2 id=\"prerequisites\">Prerequisites\u003C/h2>\u003Ca class=\"sl-anchor-link\" href=\"#prerequisites\">\u003Cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"sl-anchor-icon\">\u003Csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\u003Cpath fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\">\u003C/path>\u003C/svg>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"sr-only\" data-pagefind-ignore=\"\">Section titled “Prerequisites”\u003C/span>\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Rust 1.80+ (install via \u003Ca href=\"https://rustup.rs\">rustup\u003C/a>)\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>An API key for at least one LLM provider (Anthropic, OpenRouter, etc.)\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"sl-heading-wrapper level-h2\">\u003Ch2 id=\"clone-and-build\">Clone and build\u003C/h2>\u003Ca class=\"sl-anchor-link\" href=\"#clone-and-build\">\u003Cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"sl-anchor-icon\">\u003Csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\u003Cpath fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1